__DESCRIPTION__

You can buy the app on 
[Google Play](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.qubling.sidekick)
for Android devices, or you can check out the
[source code](https://github.com/zostay/CPAN-Sidekick) and build it yourself.

<img src="/images/cpan_sidekick.jpg" />

A couple of comments from the talk

*"Tou must read the code"* by [Masaaki Mizuno](http://people.cis.ksu.edu/~masaaki/)

The Secret to using the MetaCPAN API is to read the code!

Building JSON in Java is HARD!

Instead of trying to build JSON via gson or JSONObject, he created a micro-templating language.


See also
[(Ab)using the MetaCPAN API for Fun and Profit](/v/abusing-the-metacpan-api-for-fun-and-profit)
for a lot more details about the MetaCPAN API.


